# StaticJinjaPlus Docker Port

This repository is a port of the [StaticJinjaPlus](https://github.com/MrDave/StaticJinjaPlus) project. It contains Dockerfiles to build StaticJinjaPlus images.

Requirements:
- Docker installed on your system.

## Available base images

- `Dockerfile.ubuntu` — based on Ubuntu 22.04 (larger but more compatible)
- `Dockerfile.slim` — based on python:3.11-slim (smaller size)

## Build instructions

You can build any version by specifying the variable `REPO_URL`. Use links to archives of various versions from [original repository](https://github.com/MrDave/StaticJinjaPlus/tags), or main branch archive [url](https://github.com/MrDave/StaticJinjaPlus/archive/refs/heads/main.tar.gz).

### Build with Ubuntu
```bash
docker build -t image_name:your_image_tag \
  -f Dockerfile.ubuntu \
  --build-arg REPO_URL=https://github.com/MrDave/StaticJinjaPlus/archive/refs/tags/0.1.1.tar.gz \
  .
```

### Build with python-slim

```bash
docker build -t image_name:your_image_tag \
  -f Dockerfile.slim \
  --build-arg REPO_URL=https://github.com/MrDave/StaticJinjaPlus/archive/refs/tags/0.1.1.tar.gz \
  .
```

### Build last develop update

```bash
docker build -t image_name:your_image_tag \
  -f Dockerfile.slim \
  --build-arg REPO_URL=https://github.com/MrDave/StaticJinjaPlus/archive/refs/heads/main.tar.gz \
  .
```